description: Dedicated to bringing you a better, healthier eating experience with all the delicious flavor you crave, Granola Girl Food Truck is coming to you! These folks have a passion for good food that's good for you, made from the freshest local ingredients possible. Whether you like the Cocomo Chip shakes, Street Smart Tacos, Green Grilled Cheese, or any item off their amazing menu, you're sure to love your time with Granola Girl!
name: Granola Girl Food Truck
